                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="rubrication">
                           <foreign xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡</foreign>
                           <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢግዚአብሔር፡</foreign>
                           <foreign xml:lang="gez">መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም፡</foreign>
                           <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡</foreign>
                        </seg>
                        <desc>The Trinitarian Formula, is often abbreviated (e.g., <locus target="#2r"/>), as is Jesus ‎Christ (e.g., <locus target="#111v"/>)‎</desc>
